abstract: Caroline Wozniacki beats Andrea Petkovic to reach semifinals at Wimbledon tuneup in Eastbourne, England; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Wozniacki reached the semifinals of the Wimbledon tuneup in Eastbourne, England, beating Andrea Petkovic.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Tennis; Wozniacki Coasts in Tuneup
